-- U.S. holiday sales show steady growth - MasterCard
-- By Ramkumar Iyer in Bengaluru
-- Fri Dec 26, 2014 10:30AM EST
-- None



Dec 26 (Reuters) - The 2014 holiday season showed steady growth over the last year on strong demand for jewelry and women's apparel, according to data published by MasterCard Advisors SpendingPulse, which tracks customer spending during the holiday season.

